snippet: Ukrainian President Petro Poroshenko, condemning Russian intervention in his country, said on Saturday that there were now thousands of foreign troops and hundreds of foreign tanks in Ukraine....

headline.print_headline: President Says Hundreds of Foreign Tanks in Ukraine
headline.main: President Says Hundreds of Foreign Tanks in Ukraine

lead_paragraph: Ukrainian President Petro Poroshenko, condemning Russian intervention in his country, said on Saturday that there were now thousands of foreign troops and hundreds of foreign tanks in Ukraine.
